node.text: S/O to @1stphorm and @andyfrisella for this cool locker. Not gone lie, I got emotional when they showed it to me. I'm incredibly honored and blessed to be a part of such a great community of true American Patriots. I was genuinely blown away when I saw the HQ. Andy and all the people I met inspired me to step my game up. Plus my wife loves all of the 1st Phorm supplements. Those BBQ beef sticks are off the chain, just FYI.

node.text: A friend sent this picture of me back in my football days. There are so many emotions that come up when I see photos like this. I most often think of what could have been and at the same time grateful it never happened.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Brandon Tatum 🇺🇸 on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'SEPTEMBER 11TH, 2001 FGE FORGET'.

node.text:
“The attacks of September 11th were intended to break our spirit. Instead we have emerged stronger and more unified. We feel renewed devotion to the principles of political, economic, and religious freedom, the rule of law and respect for human life. We are more determined than ever to live our lives in freedom.” -Rudy Giuliani 🇺🇸

May we NEVER FORGET the 3,000 Americans that lost their lives this day. 

May we NEVER FORGET the brave first responders that answered the call to save their fellow man. 

May we NEVER FORGET why Freedom is a principal we must always fight for.
